===Trigger Rate===
====Double Attacks====
The cut in rate for double attacks is extremely high. Testing places the value at around 99%.

====Cut-Ins====
[[file:Base_TCI_chance.png|thumb|right|Torpedo-Cut-In chance for a non-flagship without further modifiers. Notice the slow progression beyond 50 Luck]]
<math>\text{CI %} = \left[ \dfrac{\text{Param}_\text{CI}}{\text{Const}_\text{Atk}} \right] \times 100</math>

Where:

* If luck is less than 50; <math>\text{Param}_\text{CI} = \left[ 15 + \text{Luck} + 0.75 \times \sqrt{\text{Level}} \right] + \text{Mod}_\text{flag} + \text{Mod}_\text{Damage} + \text{Mod}_\text{Equip}</math>
* If luck is 50 or greater; <math>\text{Param}_\text{CI} = \left[ 65 + \sqrt{ \left( \text{Luck} - 50 \right) } + 0.8 \times \sqrt{\text{Level}} \right] + \text{Mod}_\text{flag} + \text{Mod}_\text{Damage} + \text{Mod}_\text{Equip}</math>

* <math>\text{Const}_\text{Atk}</math> is the constant based on the attack being performed.
** Gun = <math>140</math>
** Mixed Gun = <math>130</math>
** Destroyer Mixed  = <math>130</math>
** Torpedo = <math>122</math>
** Mixed = <math>115</math>
* <math>\text{Luck}</math> is the {{Luck}} stat of the ship.
* <math>\text{Level}</math> is the level of the ship.
* <math>\text{Mod}_\text{flag}</math> is the flagship modifier of <math>15</math> if applicable. It is <math>0</math> otherwise.
* <math>\text{Mod}_\text{Damage}</math> is the damage state modifier of <math>18</math> if <span style="color:orange;">moderately damaged (中破)</span>. It is <math>0</math> otherwise.
* <math>\text{Mod}_\text{Equip}</math> are the various night battle equipment modifiers. See below for details.

